# TypeScript & React

- Prefer functional components and hooks; colocate styles (CSS modules or `src/css/`).
- Keep types explicit at API boundaries (`src/services/apiTypes/`).
- Use `strict` TypeScript; avoid `any` unless unavoidable with a short comment.
- Async: handle errors in UI; do not swallow failures in empty `catch` blocks.

```tsx
// Prefer extracted hooks for Spotify auth / API calls
export function useSpotifyLogin() { /* ... */ }
```

- Run `npm run lint` and `npm run build` after substantive changes.
